[[/div]]





[[/div]]
[[/div]]
[[/collapsible]]


[[collapsible show="+ CHAT LOGS - 05/16 (5)" hide="- ACCESS GRANTED"]]


[[div class="text-container-wrap"]]
+++ massey
[[div class="text-container"]]

[[div class="recv"]]
[[span class="text"]] heyy, wanna come over and binge those Wes Anderson films you’ve been shoving down my throat?[[/span]]
[[/div]]


[[div class="sent"]]
[[span class="text"]] Sorry, tonight can’t work. Josh is helping me with a POS art project that’s due tomorrow. He’s showing me fancy tech I can use to totally cheese this assignment. [[/span]]
[[/div]]

[[div class="recv"]]
[[span class="text"]] sounds like fun! I can always lend a hand to you guys if u need it [[/span]]
[[/div]]

[[div class="sent"]]
[[span class="text"]] thanks, but I’m pretty sure we got this in the bag. I’m free this Monday though. [[/span]]
[[/div]]

[[div class="recv"]]
[[span class="text"]] awesome. let me know if u need ANYTHING[[/span]]
[[/div]]

[[div class="sent"]]
[[span class="text"]] thanks [[/span]]
[[/div]]


[[/div]]
[[/div]]
[[/collapsible]]

[[collapsible show="+ CHAT LOGS - 05/19 (6)" hide="- ACCESS GRANTED"]]

[[div class="text-container-wrap"]]
+++ massey
[[div class="text-container"]]


[[div class="recv"]]
[[span class="text"]] Got any plans tonight? [[/span]]
[[/div]]

[[div class="sent"]]
[[span class="text"]] Yeah actually, sorry. Going to board game night with josh [[/span]]
[[/div]]


[[div class="recv"]]
[[span class="text"]] tell him your sick or something, got us tickets to the LeBron movie[[/span]]
[[/div]]

[[div class="sent"]]
[[span class="text"]] You know I’ve been meaning to see that, and I appreciate the gesture, but I wish you would tell me in advance next time[[/span]]
[[/div]]

[[div class="sent"]]
[[span class="text"]] can’t make it tonight[[/span]]
[[/div]]


[[div class="recv"]]
[[span class="text"]] all good. just find it a little odd since this is the third time this week youve completely blown me off to hangout with this josh guy. you said you wanted to be friends wtf hppned[[/span]]
[[/div]]

[[div class="recv"]]
[[span class="text"]] jkjk. Have a goodnight[[/span]]
[[/div]]

[[div class="sent"]]
[[span class="text"]] uhh you too[[/span]]
[[/div]]


[[/div]]
[[/div]]
[[/collapsible]]

[[collapsible show="+ CHAT LOGS - 06/02 (7)" hide="- ACCESS GRANTED"]]

[[div class="text-container-wrap"]]
+++ massey
[[div class="text-container"]]

[[div class="sent"]]
[[span class="text"]] Hey Mason, free this thurs for some dnd?[[/span]]
[[/div]]

[[div class="recv"]]
[[span class="text"]] sure. Hey I’ve been meaning to ask[[/span]]
[[/div]]

[[div class="sent"]]
[[span class="text"]] what’s up[[/span]]
[[/div]]

[[div class="recv"]]
[[span class="text"]] do you ever wannna give our relationship another shot? I think enough time has passed where we’ve both matured enough as individuals. I understand what I said was wrong, but I really do care about you bee. What do you say?[[/span]]
[[/div]]

[[div class="sent"]]
[[span class="text"]] So [[/span]]
[[/div]]

[[div class="sent"]]
[[span class="text"]] I should’ve told you this awhile ago- but me and josh started dating and it’s moving pretty quickly. youre one of my closest friends, and I would like to keep it that way. i cannot thank you enough for how much you’ve helped me, but I’d really like to stay friends. [[/span]]
[[/div]]

[[div class="recv"]]
[[span class="text"]] all good. Completely understand[[/span]]
[[/div]]


[[div class="recv"]]
[[span class="text"]] btw, found your old earrings. They should arrive ina few days :)[[/span]]
[[/div]]

[[div class="sent"]]
[[span class="text"]] FANTASTIC!! Never thought I’d see those things again haha, appreciate it[[/span]]
[[/div]]


[[/div]]
[[/div]]
[[/collapsible]]

Upon discovery, field agents were dispatched to Mason Dewitt’s home address. Multiple clothing items, health utilities, and electronics were absent from his room. Mason Dewitt’s body was later recovered from a nearby pond.

Investigation of his digital footprint led to the discovery of multiple illegal websites he had visited, all in relation to different methods of homicide. 




